metadata.name: Untitled Artwork
metadata.description:
Digital print created on Procreate. I am releasing this on Valentines Day purposely as I feel it can be a very 'rom com' style day and everything and every one else's life can seem more together than yours. This is a reminder that you can romanticise your own life and start to see great things happening for yourself.

Once all 25 NFT editions have sold, I will raffle off an original painted one to one of the collectors. Digital printed words and acrylic paint on A3 heavy gsm canvas paper.
